[13/04/2018 15:00:06] <font color="#ffffff">¡Qué cielo!</font>
[13/04/2018 15:00:20] <font color="#ffffff">(“Me and Julio“, Simon</font>
[13/04/2018 15:00:40] <font color="#ffffff">Estamos en Ponferrada,</font>
